This paper deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) tasks, specifically Part of Speech (POS) tagging, which falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of syntactical knowledge and computational methods to predict lexical categories of unknown words, which could be related to Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Neural Networks (cs.NE).
